songs.title: American (Cover)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: All]
Oooooh...
Oooooh...

[Verse: Lauren & (All)]
Play house, put my favorite record on
Get down, get your crystal method on
You were like tall, tan, (Oooooh...) driving ‘round the city
Flirtin’ with the girls like you’re so pretty
Springsteen is the King, (Oooooh...) don’t ya think?
I was like, "hell yeah, that guy can sing"
Like ooh-ooh-ooh-ooh-ooh (Oooooh...)
Ooh-ooh-ooh-ooh-oh

[Chorus: Camila & Ally & (Normani) & Dinah & {Lauren}]
You make me crazy, you make me wild
Just like a baby, spin me 'round like a child
Your skin so gold and brown (your skin, your skin, your skin)
Be young, be dope, be proud (be proud)
Like an American {Oooh-ooh-oooh-ooh}
Like an American {Oooh-ooh-oooh-ooh}
Like an American {Oooh-ooh-oooh-ooh}
Like an American {Oooh-ooh-oooh-ooh}
